{"id":2336,"date":"2025-04-11T01:42:41","date_gmt":"2025-04-11T01:42:41","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/?p=2336"},"modified":"2025-04-11T01:47:10","modified_gmt":"2025-04-11T01:47:10","slug":"cap-nhat-tuan-tra-quy-i-2025-thu-thach-khac-nghiet-quyet-tam-khong-lui","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/vi\/cap-nhat-tuan-tra-quy-i-2025-thu-thach-khac-nghiet-quyet-tam-khong-lui\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u1eacP NH\u1eacT TU\u1ea6N TRA QU\u00dd I\/2025: TH\u1eec TH\u00c1CH KH\u1eaeC NGHI\u1ec6T, QUY\u1ebeT T\u00c2M KH\u00d4NG LUI"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2025, \u0111\u1ed9i tu\u1ea7n tra b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 r\u1eebng (CCT) ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c cam go. Th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t c\u00f9ng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u0103n b\u1eaft gia t\u0103ng khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 r\u1eebng c\u00e0ng th\u00eam gian nan. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n v\u1eabn b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u00e1o g\u1ee1 t\u1eebng chi\u1ebfc b\u1eaby, ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y t\u1eebng l\u00e1n tr\u1ea1i, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 s\u1ef1 s\u1ed1ng n\u01a1i r\u1eebng s\u00e2u.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-2338 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/HARSH-CHALLENGES-UNWAVERING-DETERMINATION-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"374\" height=\"374\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/HARSH-CHALLENGES-UNWAVERING-DETERMINATION-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/HARSH-CHALLENGES-UNWAVERING-DETERMINATION-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/HARSH-CHALLENGES-UNWAVERING-DETERMINATION-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/HARSH-CHALLENGES-UNWAVERING-DETERMINATION-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/HARSH-CHALLENGES-UNWAVERING-DETERMINATION-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/HARSH-CHALLENGES-UNWAVERING-DETERMINATION-2048x2048.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 374px) 100vw, 374px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>Th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t, tu\u1ea7n tra gian nan<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m, th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft t\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c tu\u1ea7n tra di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng: l\u1ea1nh c\u1eaft da, m\u01b0a tr\u00e1i m\u00f9a k\u00e9o d\u00e0i, gi\u00f3 l\u1edbn l\u00e0m c\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed5 ch\u1eafn l\u1ed1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tu\u1ea7n tra \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi v\u00f4 v\u00e0n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o \u01b0\u1edbt s\u0169ng, b\u1eefa \u0103n ngu\u1ed9i l\u1ea1nh gi\u1eefa r\u1eebng s\u00e2u kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m ch\u00f9n b\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng con ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eadn t\u00e2m.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1eb7c cho th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i, \u0111\u1ed9i CCT v\u1eabn ki\u00ean tr\u00ec ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. Ch\u1ec9 trong qu\u00fd I, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tu\u1ea7n tra 230km \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eebng, th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 134 gi\u1edd tu\u1ea7n tra, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ecdi hi\u1ec3m nguy \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c lo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt hoang d\u00e3.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00c1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb b\u1eaby s\u0103n v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00ed h\u1eadu<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t tu\u1ea7n tra cho th\u1ea5y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u0103n b\u1eaft t\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c v\u1eabn \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a b\u1eaby d\u00e2y v\u00e0 b\u1eaby k\u1eb9p \u2013 nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 s\u0103n b\u1eaft nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eadt v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n ho\u1eb7c gi\u1ebft ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt hoang d\u00e3.<\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00ed h\u1eadu c\u0169ng g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn. Th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tu\u1ea7n tra m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0m thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eadp t\u00ednh di c\u01b0 v\u00e0 sinh s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u lo\u00e0i, khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang d\u1ec5 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a th\u1ee3 s\u0103n.<\/p>\n<p>H\u01a1n 400 b\u1eaby \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e1o g\u1ee1, ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y l\u00e1n tr\u1ea1i th\u1ee3 s\u0103n<\/p>\n<p>D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi mu\u00f4n v\u00e0n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, \u0111\u1ed9i CCT v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong qu\u00fd I\/2025:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>406<\/strong> b\u1eaby c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e1o g\u1ee1, gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u lo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt qu\u00fd hi\u1ebfm<\/li>\n<li><strong>6<\/strong> l\u00e1n tr\u1ea1i th\u1ee3 s\u0103n b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y, c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t m\u1eaft x\u00edch trong chu\u1ed7i s\u0103n b\u1eaft tr\u00e1i ph\u00e9p<\/li>\n<li><strong>1<\/strong> kh\u1ea9u s\u00fang s\u0103n t\u1ef1 ch\u1ebf b\u1ecb thu gi\u1eef, gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u nguy c\u01a1 s\u0103n b\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt hoang d\u00e3<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-2405 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6248595342871_b477f9f6f395b7138aa7005e0ddd922a-1-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"455\" height=\"341\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6248595342871_b477f9f6f395b7138aa7005e0ddd922a-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6248595342871_b477f9f6f395b7138aa7005e0ddd922a-1-1024x767.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6248595342871_b477f9f6f395b7138aa7005e0ddd922a-1-768x575.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6248595342871_b477f9f6f395b7138aa7005e0ddd922a-1.jpg 1276w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 455px) 100vw, 455px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i CCT tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 r\u1eebng.<\/p>\n<p aria-level=\"3\"><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">\u0110\u1ed9i CCT ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u2013 C\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 chung tay c\u1ee7a c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng<\/span><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;134245529&quot;:true,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:281,&quot;335559739&quot;:281}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">\u0110\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 r\u1eebng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt hoang d\u00e3, \u0111\u1ed9i CCT c\u1ea7n th\u00eam s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f4i gi\u00e0y r\u00e1ch, nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o s\u0169ng n\u01b0\u1edbc hay nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00eam ng\u1ee7 r\u1eebng l\u1ea1nh bu\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i xa h\u01a1n.\u00a0<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i CCT b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch:<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"14\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">\u1ee6ng h\u1ed9 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh ho\u1eb7c trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"14\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Lan t\u1ecfa th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 r\u1eebng<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;3355516